Abu Dhabi
Provide advice and support to Executive Regulatory Affairs Director on all matters related to the responsibilities of the Regulatory Affairs Directorate. 1. Advise the Executive Regulatory Affairs Management. 2. Regulatory Affairs Organization Management. 3. Budget. 4. HSE. 5. Stakeholder Engagement. 6. People Management.
Skills
1. Leadership and team building. 2. Understanding of power plant operation and associated regulatory requirements. 3. Project management skills. 4. Negotiation skills. 5. Ability to manage effectively across functions. 6. Analytical/technical mindset. 7. Strong English writing skills. 8. English fluency.
